IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User texhewson@gmail.com
# We will use a script to feed the token to mbsync
PassCmd "~/configs/scripts/get-gmail-refresh-token.sh"
AuthMechs XOAUTH2
SSLType IMAPS

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/Mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/Mail/gmail/INBOX

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns INBOX "[Gmail]/Enviados" "[Gmail]/Todos" "[Gmail]/Papelera" "[Gmail]/Borradores" Personal Work Spanish holiday
Create Near
SyncState *
